  "intent_precise": "Tecan Cortisol ELISA w/ Heater Shaker: Using working_plate (labware, slot 2), samples (plate, slot 1), reagents (deep_well_plate, slot 4), wash (deep_well_plate, slot 5). With heater_shaker module. (1) Mix 2 times. (2) Transfer from source to destination. (3) Transfer from source to destination. (4) Close heater-shaker latch. (5) Shake at s_speed RPM. (6) Pause for incubation. (7) Pause for incubation. (8) Open heater-shaker latch. (9) Pause: Move the ELISA Plate to the Shaker (10) Close heater-shaker latch. (11) Transfer from sample A1 to eia A1. (12) Mix 2 times. (13) Transfer from wash (A1, A1) to eia (A1, A1). (14) Mix 2 times. (15) Transfer from source A1 to eia A1. (16) Mix 2 times. (17) Transfer from source A1 to eia A1. (18) Open heater-shaker latch. (19) Pause: Move the ELISA Plate to the Reader",
